HEADWORD: Irrespectively
<hw>Ir`re*spec"tive*ly</hw>
<pr>(⟦icr⟧r`r⟦esl⟧*sp⟦ecr⟧k"t⟦icr⟧v*l⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<def>Without regard to conditions; not taking circumstances into
consideration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Prosperity, considered absolutely and <qex>irrespectively</qex>,
is better and more desirable than adversity.</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Irrespirable</ent>⟦br⟧
